{"text_id":134091,"tokens":["Summer"," projects"," are"," important"," because"," it"," is"," during"," this"," time"," when"," many"," people"," take"," advantage"," of"," their"," free"," time"," by"," relaxing"," or"," spending"," more"," quality"," time"," with"," family"," members","."," However",","," there"," can"," still"," be"," value"," added"," if"," you"," design"," your"," own"," personalized"," summer"," project",".","\n","One"," way"," to"," do"," so"," would"," be"," through"," self","-","directed"," learning","."," Self","-","directed"," learning"," refers"," to"," any"," activity"," where"," individuals"," set"," goals"," on"," what"," needs"," to"," be"," accomplished"," within"," a"," certain"," period"," of"," time"," (","e",".","g",".,"," one"," month",")"," and"," then"," work"," towards"," accomplishing"," those"," goals"," without"," being"," told"," exactly"," which"," steps"," need"," to"," be"," taken","."," This"," type"," of"," learning"," has"," been"," shown"," to"," have"," several"," benefits"," including"," increased"," motivation",","," improved"," self","-","esteem"," and"," better"," academic"," performance",".","\n","Another"," benefit"," associated"," with"," self","-","directed"," learning"," is"," its"," ability"," to"," promote"," lifelong"," learning"," skills","."," Lif","elong"," learning"," skills"," refer","..."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"bloomz","label":1}